00:20:17.380 --> 00:20:19.140
if we merge the meetings?

00:20:20.140 --> 00:20:22.619
Now, then one Wednesday, I think it was about 330

00:20:22.619 --> 00:20:23.460
in the afternoon.

00:20:23.460 --> 00:20:26.299
We'd had a long meeting.

00:20:26.299 --> 00:20:30.660
