00:21:07.299 --> 00:21:10.539
all of the meetings, including the book study,

00:21:10.539 --> 00:21:15.140
but they're very poor and they couldn't afford the bus fare

00:21:15.180 --> 00:21:17.940
to attend two midweek meetings.

00:21:17.940 --> 00:21:19.579
They had to choose.

00:21:19.579 --> 00:21:22.380
And if they attended the school and service meeting,

00:21:22.380 --> 00:21:25.579
they could get almost two hours of spiritual direction

00:21:25.579 --> 00:21:28.940
