00:21:31.339 --> 00:21:34.660
and service meeting that won out.

00:21:34.660 --> 00:21:39.660
While those two letters put a real face on the situation

00:21:40.339 --> 00:21:42.779
and it helped us to make the decision.

00:21:43.779 --> 00:21:47.779
Now in 2008, a public edition and a study edition

00:21:47.779 --> 00:21:50.779
of the Watchtower began to be published.

00:21:50.779 --> 00:21:54.779
That decision was a long time coming.

00:21:54.779 --> 00:21:57.779
