00:21:59.779 --> 00:22:02.779
let's wait a little bit, let's see what Jehovah wants.

00:22:02.779 --> 00:22:06.779
The main thing was, what would Jehovah want?

00:22:06.779 --> 00:22:08.779
And how would we know?

00:22:09.380 --> 00:22:12.980
We decided to make a sort of fleece test.

00:22:12.980 --> 00:22:17.980
And so in 2006, we began publishing one awake a month

00:22:18.660 --> 00:22:20.500
