00:22:32.059 --> 00:22:34.660
we'll know that Jehovah is not backing this arrangement.

00:22:34.660 --> 00:22:38.180
We can go back to producing two awakes a year.

00:22:38.940 --> 00:22:41.019
Well, what was the result?

00:22:41.019 --> 00:22:43.339
At the end of the year, we were placing

00:22:43.339 --> 00:22:46.619
as many magazines at three per month

00:22:46.619 --> 00:22:51.059
as we had been placing at four per month the year before.

00:22:51.059 --> 00:22:55.460
