00:47:24.039 --> 00:47:26.280
But I was willing to do that.

00:47:26.280 --> 00:47:28.039
I knew what I wanted to do.

00:47:28.039 --> 00:47:31.659
I did it.

00:47:31.659 --> 00:47:36.099
